  <a href="/coleccion" class="flex flex-col justify-center justify-items-center items-center hover:bg-color2 focus:bg-color2 px-5 pt-10 pb-8 rounded-xl font-bold text-center text-xl lg:text-2xl cursor-pointer align-middle">Colección</a>
